<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
{% include '_partials/seo' with { legacyTemplate: 'full-service-parts.html' } %}
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Saira:ital,wght@0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;1,600;1,700;1,800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="kikers.css?v=20260713-craftcms3">
</head>
<body id="top">

{% include '_partials/site-header' with { thirdNav: 'request', thirdHref: '#request', ctaLabel: 'Request a Part', ctaHref: '#request' } %}

<nav class="crumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><div class="wrap"><a href="index.html">Home</a><span class="sep">›</span><span>Full-Service Parts</span></div></nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero compact" id="top-hero">
  <div class="hero-photo ph ph--dark"><div class="ph-tag"><span class="kk">📷 HERO BACKGROUND</span><span class="d">Staff at the counter pulling/handing over a part — friendly, daylight.</span></div></div>
  <div class="wrap"><div class="hero-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="h-tags"><span class="eyebrow on-ink">Full-Service Parts</span><span class="chiplet">We pull it for you</span></div>
      <h1>Need a part pulled <em>for you?</em></h1>
      <p class="lede">Not every job is a DIY job. Tell us the part and the vehicle, and we'll check our yard and the nationwide parts network to track it down. Quality used and OEM parts, tested and ready. Call <a href="tel:{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber|replace({"-": ""}) }}" style="color:#fff;text-decoration:underline">{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</a> or send a request.</p>
      <div class="cta-row"><a class="btn btn--amber btn--lg" href="tel:{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber|replace({"-": ""}) }}"><span class="ic">📞</span>Call {{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</a><a class="btn btn--outline-light btn--lg" href="#request">Request a Part</a></div>
    </div>
    <div class="offer-card" id="request-mini">
      <div class="ohead"><h2>Request a part</h2></div>
      <div class="sub">Tell us what you need — we'll track it down.</div>
      <form class="qf" onsubmit="return submitMsg(event)">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Year, make &amp; model" required>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Part needed (e.g. alternator)" required>
        <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone" required>
        <button class="btn btn--filled btn--block" type="submit"><span class="ic">→</span>Send Request</button>
      </form>
      <div class="fine">We'll call or text you back fast</div>
    </div>
  </div></div>
</section>
<div class="hazard"></div>

<!-- SELF VS FULL -->
<section class="sec">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head center"><span class="eyebrow">Two Ways to Get Your Part</span><h2 style="font-style:italic">Pull it yourself, or let us</h2><p>Same yard, same savings — your call on who does the wrenching.</p></div>
    <div class="paths">
      <div class="path">
        <div class="ph ph--16x9"><div class="ph-in"><span class="ph-cam">📷</span><span class="ph-kick">PHOTO — SELF-SERVE</span><span class="ph-desc">Customer pulling a part with their own tools in a row.</span></div></div>
        <div class="pbody">
          <div class="ic">🔧</div><h3>Self-Serve (U-Pull)</h3>
          <p>Lowest price. Come in, find your vehicle by row, and pull the part yourself.</p>
          <ul><li><span class="c">✓</span> Best pricing</li><li><span class="c">✓</span> Bring your own tools</li><li><span class="c">✓</span> Open Mon-Fri 9-4:30; Sat 8-2</li></ul>
          <a class="btn btn--ink btn--block" href="u-pull-parts.html" style="margin-top:auto"><span class="ic">→</span>Search the Yard</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="path">
        <div class="ph ph--16x9"><div class="ph-in"><span class="ph-cam">📷</span><span class="ph-kick">PHOTO — FULL-SERVICE</span><span class="ph-desc">A pulled, tested part on the counter ready for pickup.</span></div></div>
        <div class="pbody">
          <div class="ic">📦</div><h3>Full-Service</h3>
          <p>We do the pulling. Tell us the part and we'll locate it, pull it, and have it ready.</p>
          <ul><li><span class="c">✓</span> We pull &amp; test it</li><li><span class="c">✓</span> We check the nationwide network</li><li><span class="c">✓</span> Pickup at the counter</li></ul>
          <a class="btn btn--filled btn--block" href="#request" style="margin-top:auto"><span class="ic">→</span>Request a Part</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="sec" style="background:var(--surface-3)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head center"><span class="eyebrow">How It Works</span><h2>Tell us · We find it · You pick up</h2></div>
    <div class="steps3">
      <div class="stepc"><div class="node">1</div><h3>Tell Us the Part</h3><p>Year, make, model and the part you need. Call or send the form.</p></div>
      <div class="stepc"><div class="node">2</div><h3>We Track It Down</h3><p>We check our yard first, then the nationwide used-parts network if needed.</p></div>
      <div class="stepc"><div class="node">3</div><h3>Pick It Up</h3><p>We pull and test it, then have it ready at the counter.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- REQUEST FORM -->
<section class="sec" id="request">
  <div class="wrap"><div class="split2 top">
    <div class="info">
      <span class="eyebrow">Request a Part</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(23px,3vw,31px);margin:8px 0 10px;font-style:italic">Can't find it? We'll look.</h2>
      <p class="lead-p">Give us the details and we'll check our inventory and the broader network. The more you can tell us — trim, engine size, part number — the faster we'll match it.</p>
      <div class="qline"><span class="ic">📞</span><span><b><a href="tel:{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber|replace({"-": ""}) }}">{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</a></b><span class="s">Fastest way to reach us — Mon-Fri, 9 to 4:30; Sat, 8 to 2</span></span></div>
      <div class="qline" style="border-bottom:none"><span class="ic">🌐</span><span><b>Nationwide parts network</b><span class="s">We can source from the national used-parts system. <span class="tagph">link the car-part.com / Crush resource</span></span></span></div>
    </div>
    <form class="form-card" onsubmit="return submitMsg(event)">
      <div class="grid2" style="margin-bottom:16px"><div class="field"><label>Year</label><input placeholder="2012" required></div><div class="field"><label>Make</label><input placeholder="Honda" required></div></div>
      <div class="grid2" style="margin-bottom:16px"><div class="field"><label>Model</label><input placeholder="Civic" required></div><div class="field"><label>Part needed</label><input placeholder="Alternator" required></div></div>
      <div class="grid2" style="margin-bottom:16px"><div class="field"><label>Name</label><input placeholder="First &amp; last" required></div><div class="field"><label>Phone</label><input type="tel" placeholder="(850) 000-0000" required></div></div>
      <div class="field" style="margin-bottom:18px"><label>Details (optional)</label><textarea placeholder="Trim, engine size, part number, anything that helps…"></textarea></div>
      <button class="btn btn--filled btn--block btn--lg" type="submit"><span class="ic">→</span>Send My Part Request</button>
      <div class="disclaim">We'll call or text you back during business hours.</div>
    </form>
  </div></div>
</section>

<div class="race-rule"></div>
<section class="finalcta"><div class="wrap">
  <div><h2>Looking for a part? Let's find it.</h2><p>Quality used and OEM parts — pulled, tested, and ready. Call or send a request.</p></div>
  <div class="grp"><a class="btn btn--amber btn--lg" href="tel:{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber|replace({"-": ""}) }}"><span class="ic">📞</span>Call {{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }}</a><a class="btn btn--outline-light btn--lg" href="#request">Request a Part</a></div>
</div></section>

{% include '_partials/site-footer' %}

<div class="toast-host" id="toastHost" aria-live="polite"></div>
